pageTitle: Prof. Maria Goretti Sanyu Nassali Musoke

widgetsleft.data:
MARIA GORETTI SANYU NASSALI MUSOKE (Prof)
Membership No.: 595
Birthday Anniversary: 19th January
Marital Status: Widow
Profession(s): Information scientist
Occupation(s):
  • University Professor
Current place(s) of work:
  • Kyambogo University - (Deputy Vice Chancellor Academic Affairs )
Outstanding Achievement(s) including PPSCL club positions:
  • First female Chair of PP IV Social Club - (2017)
  • First female Professor of Information Science in Uganda - (2010)
  • First female Deputy Vice Chancellor at Kyambogo University - (2018)
  • First Ugandan female to head Makerere Univ Library Services - (2004 - 2014)
  • Authored a book titled Informed and healthy: theoretical and applied perspectives on the value of information to health care, 2016, Academic Press - Elsevier -(2016)
Clubs/ Organizations that you are associated with:
  1. Pope Paul VI S Club
  2. Uganda National Academy of Sciences
  3. Kisubi University Council

  • Trinity College Nabbingo S1 S6

  • University of Wales, Aberythwyth, Masters

Hobbies:

Other Information: A proud Catholic. I am a mother of two; motherhood is a pleasant and God given experience.
